Yes, I do have trouble making friends and are often viewed as a weirdo by others, but that doesn’t give you the right to say stuff like that! Whoever you are, you are a disgrace to the human race and are slowing down countless efforts to support people like myself! Hopefully if you read this comment it sends a clear message to you about how what you say can affect others and you will view it as a learning experience.
